events.text:
You did some research.
Although, yes, your dreams remind you of the shoot'em'ups you used to play...
They're really more akin to bullet hell games.
(Which, to be fair, is a subgenre of shoot'em'up.)
But that's not really the interesting part.
You discovered that bullet hells have mythological precedence.
All throughout the world, but more concetrated in Japan, mythological creatures have been described as attacking with barrages of projectiles.
It's usually not very relevant to myths, but...
It's there.
Could it be...?
